displayChart.description: Your weekly update of the most popular tracks in Chandigarh, India.

labels.name: Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd.

highlights.text: Sidhu Moose Wala has the most spots on Top Songs Chandigarh. Never Fold is the highest at #10.
Excuses by AP Dhillon, Gurinder Gill, and Intense has been on Top Songs Chandigarh the longest, at 67 weeks straight.
Faizal by Varinder Brar is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Chandigarh, up 33 spots at #56.
Rutba by Satinder Sartaaj is the highest new entry on Top Songs Chandigarh at #44.
